      <title>Disneyland One-Day vs Annual Passport Prices Over Time: 1981 to 2019 (adjusted for 2020 dollars)</title>
      <link>http://localhost:1313/2020/disneyland-one-day-vs-annual-passport-prices-over-time-1981-to-2019-adjusted-for-2020-dollars/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 25 Jan 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
